  "texts": [
    "In the next step, input Ground Control Points (GCPs), i.e., markers with known coordinates, are defined to geo-reference.",
    "At this stage, error resolution is also computed.",
    "A sparse point cloud is consequently generated using Structure from Motion (SfM), followed by a denser cloud that is created by Multi-view Stereo (MVS), with a metric value.",
    "In this phase, for each image, the corresponding depth map is calculated.",
    "Dense point cloud can be extracted and stored in.las or.laz file format for further processing."
  ],
